        <div class="row padding">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="~/import/img/images.jpg" class="card-img-top">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Nepal Police</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            The police of Nepal is responsible for maintaining law and order and prevention of
                            crime according to the constitution of Nepal and is under the authority of the Ministry of Home Affairs.
                            Sarbendra Khanal is the current IGP of Nepal Police
                        </p>
